1. Moj *uloga* u ovom projektu je da koordiniram tim. (My *role* in this project is to coordinate the team.)
2. Kako biste ocenili glumačku *ulogu* glavnog lika u ovom filmu? (How would you rate the actor's *role* of the main character in this movie?)
3. Ona ima važnu *ulogu* u našoj kompaniji. (She has an important *position* in our company.)
4. Uložio je veliku *ulogu* u ovaj posao. (He invested a large *sum of money* in this business.)
5. *Uloga* žena u društvu se vremenom menjala. (The *role* of women in society has changed over time.)
6. Ovaj glumac je dobio mnoge važne *uloge* u pozorištu. (This actor has received many important *roles* in the theater.)
7. Kako biste opisali *ulogu* umetnosti u našim životima? (How would you describe the *role* of art in our lives?)
8. Molim vas da mi dodelite neku *ulogu* u vašoj predstavi. (Please assign me some *role* in your play.)
9. Potrebno je da razumemo *uloge* svih učesnika u ovom procesu. (It's necessary to understand the *roles* of all participants in this process.)
10. U ovom filmu, glumac igra *ulogu* detektiva koji istražuje zločin. (In this movie, the actor plays the *part* of a detective who investigates a crime.)